---
title: Tex-Mex Spiced Chicken & Spinach Rice with Avocado Salsa & Mayo
description: This colourful Tex-Mex dish ticks every box. With a warming spice blend, plus creamy mayo and speedy rice with spinach stirred through,
your tastebuds are fully catered for, as they should be!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-spiced-chicken-spinach-rice-0272b421.jpg
